{"tid":2237239,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"英議員促賀知義拒絕港任命","createTime":"2020-10-10T05:53:55.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-10T05:53:55.000Z","uid":25558,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"13fcd6d2b91257702482d0ece243116fda74b8d0","tid":2237239,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-10T05:53:55.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201010/JIPPQXYLNVDGDD7HGGFOE57IIE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201010%2FJIPPQXYLNVDGDD7HGGFOE57IIE%2F&d=qh2qPVBUtyR5HqmPKg%2BIDHd5d2ehbLCfOFFYxDFDkZk%3D&h=efa41065\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2F20201010%2FJIPPQXYLNVDGDD7HGGFOE57IIE%2F&h=0434872c\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/local/20201010/JIPPQXYLNVDGDD7HGGFOE57IIE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n英議員促賀知義拒絕港任命<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/fGPJNtVuk4GFuGpO8dGqLeRq_5w=/1329x886/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/7WDTIMK6BFFM7MLYNWX6QSXB2U.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2FfGPJNtVuk4GFuGpO8dGqLeRq_5w%3D%2F1329x886%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2F7WDTIMK6BFFM7MLYNWX6QSXB2U.jpg&h=b8eb45b9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n■英國最高法院副院長賀知義獲薦為本港終院非常任法官。<br />\n<br />\n【本報訊】終審法院非常任法官施覺民上月初疑因不滿港版國安法突然辭任，。。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n聯署信由32名跨黨派議員包括上議院議員奧爾頓勳爵（Lord Alton of Liverpool）、保守黨申克溫勳爵（Lord Shinkwin）等及團體「Fight for Freedom. Stand with Hong Kong」發出。<br />\n<br />\n公開信指出，英國外交大臣已表明港版國安法違反國際條約，否認人權和言論自由。港版國安法是服從於中共《國家安全法》，林鄭月娥要求香港法院任命一位傑出人士，圖使其司法系統的「獨立性」合法化。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n指任命損害司法制度聲譽<br />\n<br />\n議員認為，賀知義接受任命不僅使英國法官參與了香港當局實施的侵犯人權行為，更等同承認港版國安法有缺陷的原則和程序，使英國獨立的司法系統因為這種聯繫或招致聲譽受損。大法官兼司法大臣需要就任命作出清晰明確的回應，表明英國法院法官不宜接受香港法院的職位。"}]}